    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Welcome to <a href="https://hexo.io/">Hexo</a>! This is your veryfirst post. Check <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/">documentation</a> formore info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find theanswer in <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html">troubleshooting</a> oryou can ask me on <a href="https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues">GitHub</a>.</p><h2 id="quick-start">Quick Start</h2><h3 id="create-a-new-post">Create a new post</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><i class="iconfont icon-icon-down" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse-twpiazlik6p0v1"></i><span>bash</span><div class="collapse show" id="collapse-twpiazlik6p0v1"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ hexo new <span class="hljs-string">"My New Post"</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html">Writing</a></p><h3 id="run-server">Run server</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><i class="iconfont icon-icon-down" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse-ivktd5lik6p0v1"></i><span>bash</span><div class="collapse show" id="collapse-ivktd5lik6p0v1"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ hexo server<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/server.html">Server</a></p><h3 id="generate-static-files">Generate static files</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><i class="iconfont icon-icon-down" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse-pg8jgxlik6p0v1"></i><span>bash</span><div class="collapse show" id="collapse-pg8jgxlik6p0v1"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ hexo generate<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html">Generating</a></p><h3 id="deploy-to-remote-sites">Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><i class="iconfont icon-icon-down" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse-5b48kvlik6p0v1"></i><span>bash</span><div class="collapse show" id="collapse-5b48kvlik6p0v1"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ hexo deploy<br></code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html">Deployment</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
